{%- comment %}
================================================================================
Schema: FAQPage - Business FAQs (AEO Transactional Bridge)
================================================================================
Purpose:   Declares the Bastelschachtel FAQ page with structured Q&A.
            FAQ schema pages earn significantly more AI Overview citations.
Type:      FAQPage with Question + Answer entities
Scope:     /pages/faq-haufig-fragen only - via theme.liquid conditional
Created:   2026-04-13
Version:   FORTRESS (2026-04-13)

Key Features:
- HTML <a> links INSIDE acceptedAnswer.text (Transactional Bridge)
- Product URLs pulled DYNAMICALLY from all_products (no hardcoded handles)
- Links point to live product/info pages
- acceptedAnswer.text matches visible FAQ page HTML exactly
- SpamBrain defense: verbatim reconciliation between schema and visible text
- ASCII-safe encoding (no umlaut literals in strings)

Transactional Bridge Links:
- Versandkosten        -> /pages/versandkosten
- Widerrufsrecht      -> /pages/widerrufsrecht
- Lagerverfuegbarkeit -> /products/glasaetzungspaste-50ml (dynamic)
- Zahlungsmethoden    -> /pages/zahlungsmethoden
- Kundenservice       -> /pages/kontakt
================================================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment %} Dynamic product URL resolution -- prevents stale handles {%- endcomment -%}
